## Engine 5a2 follow-ups

The 5a2 round ships the plan-stage type surface + stub function
signatures; every algorithm step is `todo!()`. Each entry below is
a separate downstream micro-round that fills in one step's body.

- Step 1: DAG construction from AccessMask overlap
  (`plan::build_dag`).
- Step 2: Topological sort + node renumbering
  (`plan::topo_sort`).
- Step 3: Upward rank + critical path
