- Step 9: Per-fiber morsel sizing
  (`plan::size_morsels`).
- Step 10: Per-phase adaptive configs
  (`plan::adaptive_config`).
- Step 11: Column classification per fiber
  (`plan::classify_columns`).
- Step 12: Dirty propagation masks for incremental skip
  (`plan::propagate_dirty`).
- Swap AccessMask bit-backing for arvo-bitmask once const-generic
